  "sourceCode": "Employer Portal",
  "title": "Executive Housekeeper",
  "description": "<ul>\n  <li>He/She is committed to providing the highest levels of comfort and hospitality to guests, which leads to achieving maximum guest satisfaction and organisational profitability.<br>\n</li>\n  <li>Assist in creating standard operating procedures for operations, keeping in line with the hotel’s service standards. Assist in budgeting and control on expenses. He/She also needs to oversee inventory checks.<br>\n</li>\n  <li>Assist in handling all staff matters, including hiring and training. He/She assist in resolving issues and directs teams to meet the hotel’s standards. He/She also shows a high level of organisational awareness and leadership skills. </li>\n</ul>\n<p><strong>ESSENTIAL DUTIES AND RESPONSIBILITIES</strong>:</p>\n<ul>\n  <li>Assist in analysing and recommending best practices and technologies in hospitality</li>\n  <li>Assist in applying systems thinking to resolve problems and make effective decisions</li>\n  <li>Assist in assessing and reviewing hospitality data</li>\n  <li>Assist in developing innovations to enhance customer experience</li>\n  <li>Assist in designing and developing a productivity framework</li>\n  <li>Assist in developing self to maintain professional competence at a senior management level</li>\n  <li>Assist in managing crisis situations</li>\n  <li>Assist in driving service quality and customer satisfaction</li>\n  <li>Assist in leading managers to develop organisational and governance strategies</li>\n  <li>Assist in managing and directing negotiations</li>\n  <li>Assist in managing assets and inventory</li>\n  <li>Assist in managing the budgeting and forecasting processes</li>\n  <li>Assist in managing cross-functional and culturally diverse teams</li>\n  <li>Assist in managing the housekeeping department’s human resources</li>\n  <li>Assist in managing quality systems and processes</li>\n  <li>Assist in managing resource planning</li>\n  <li>Assist in preparing budgets for the business unit</li>\n  <li>Assist in providing information for management decision-making</li>\n  <li>Assist in striving for service excellence to drive customer loyalty</li>\n</ul>",
